Package: mobileRNA
Type: Package
Title: Explore sRNAs population changes & canditate foreign mobile sRNAs
Version: 0.99.9
Authors@R: c(person("Katie", "Jeynes-Cupper", 
    email = "kej031@student.bham.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre")),
    person("Marco", "Catoni", email = "m.catoni@bham.ac.uk", role = "aut"))
Description: The mobileRNA package allows for the identifcation of mobile small 
  RNA molecules in plant graft systems or other chimeric systems, and allows for
  typical sRNAseq analysis between treatment and control conditions. 
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Depends:
    R (>= 4.0)
